{"tid":1710151,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"YG冇左BIG BANG 見30億韓元赤字","createTime":"2019-11-12T05:47:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T06:35:12.000Z","uid":74065,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5672e4cca421aa4a1cffbb938ca04ef9c9757262","tid":1710151,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T05:47:28.000Z","msg":"[YG第三季度30億韓元赤字，BIGBANG若續約明年最大收益300億韓元]<br />\n據11日YG公開數據顯示，其第三季度營業損失約30億韓元，比去年同期（營業利潤約26億韓元）相比轉變為赤字。同時據韓亞金融投資研究員表示&ldquo;YG愛豆組合回歸不足，除了BLACKPINK泰國巡演以外沒有特別的收益活動。第四季度將反映樂童音樂家和WINNER回歸的音源收益，而BLACKPINK看起來要明年才能回歸，多少會有些遺憾的業績。&rdquo; <br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;現在BIGBANG是否會續約還是不明朗，關於楊賢碩前YG代表的嫌疑也在調查中。若是依靠BIGBANG續約-BLACKPINK&amp;TREASURE 13，明年還是會成為最具上升潛力的企劃社。<br />\n<br />\nBIGBANG續約的話明年最高營業利潤或達300億韓元。&rdquo; &ldquo;有依據判斷TREASURE 13依然是有機會的，其中包含4名日本成員，明年日本國民組合'嵐'即將隱退，在日本市場很可能與'PD101'Japan展開競爭。&rdquo;"},{"pid":"028cd55072fce89e7ce9d2301f49fed591bf8acb","tid":1710151,"uid":229026,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T05:55:42.000Z","msg":"Bigbang自己開公司好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a33e7f6951c90b7926ce3d48b2e8e3b25e54ab8","tid":1710151,"uid":52073,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T06:18:17.000Z","msg":"yg呢啲垃圾執撚左佢啦"},{"pid":"f141d6eff85d8b2dc5b3a278023570543e6cb5cb","tid":1710151,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a33e7f6951c90b7926ce3d48b2e8e3b25e54ab8","tid":1710151,"uid":52073,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T06:18:17.000Z","msg":"yg呢啲垃圾執撚左佢啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T06:25:38.000Z","msg":"你同佢一齊"},{"pid":"034ab41c03adecd1aaa8c2b8b991ae445fc10a90","tid":1710151,"uid":323791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T06:29:16.000Z","msg":"而家三大係咪sm jyp同bighit<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0af8e750b575828f783ef7438a07775d7063ab9c","tid":1710151,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s